# Provider key fallback (optional). BYOK is the default: the app reads the key
# from the `x-provider-key` request header and never persists it. Set this only
# if you want a server-side default for local development.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# The example "search" tool returns canned results so the template runs with no
# external API. To wire a real web search, add your provider key here and
# implement the call in lib/agents.ts.
# TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...
